&gt; USER PID %CPU %MEM VSZ RSS TTY STAT START TIME COMMAND
&gt; ...
&gt; bart 7911 2.0 0.0 0 0 ? Zl 09:50 0:03 [java]
&gt; &lt;defunct&gt;
&gt; ...
